    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change rules so private hire vehicles can't refuse a short journey",
        "additional_details": "Multiple times I\u2019ve been left waiting because of cancelled private hire vehicles, due to drivers cancelling. I\u2019ve had conversations with drivers over this issue, and with the ongoing emphasis on female safety I believe this is a highly topical issue.",
        "background": "Don't allow private hire vehicles to refuse short journeys, so people in need to get home are not left stranded.",
